<p>I have test with parameter like this:</p>  <pre><code>class Test {    [Test, Category("somecategory")]    public void SomeTest([ValueSource(typeof(Data), "Variants")] string variants)    {        // code for test    } }  class Data {    public string[] Variants()    {       string[] variants = new string[] { "a", "b" };       return variants;    } } </code></pre>  <p>I need to add Category based on ValueSource of test. If test is using variant <i>a</i>, it have category <i>a</i>. So it can be started separately in NUnit console.</p>